             if (response.body() != null) {
                 OderResult result = xmlToResult(response.body());
                 if (result.getReturn_code().equals("SUCCESS")) {
                     if (result.getResult_code().equals("SUCCESS")) {

                     }
                 } else {

                 }
             }

         }

         @Override
         public void onFailure(Call<String> call, Throwable t) {

         }
     });
```
